  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the curry powder and garam masala and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the miso paste and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the diced Korean pear and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the lime juice and vegetable broth and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve hot over rice or with naan bread."
